<table>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td>
<h3> Sla Timalapse configurations</h3>
<div class="control-group">
    <label class="control-label" for="gpio_pin">GPIO Pin Number:</label>
    <div class="controls">
        <input type="number" class="form-control input-sm" style="width: 50px;" id="gpio_pin" min="0" max="40" step="1" data-bind="value: settings.plugins.slatimelapse.gpio_pin">
        <span class="info-icon">
		    <a href="https://pinout.xyz/" target="_blank" class="same-color">
		        <img src="/plugin/slatimelapse/static/img/info.png" alt="Information">
		    </a>
		</span>
        <p class="help-block">Enter the BCM GPIO pin number (0-40) for your setup.</p>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="control-group">
    <label class="control-label" for="photo_delay">Photo Delay (seconds):</label>
    <div class="controls">
        <input type="number" class="form-control input-sm" style="width: 50px;" id="photo_delay" min="1" step="1" data-bind="value: settings.plugins.slatimelapse.photo_delay">
        <span class="info-icon">
            <a href="#" class="same-color" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#helpModal"> <!-- Added data-toggle and data-target attributes -->
                <img src="/plugin/slatimelapse/static/img/info.png" alt="Information">
            </a>
        </span>
        <p class="help-block">Enter the delay between photos (in seconds).</p>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- Modal -->
<div class="modal fade" id="helpModal" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="helpModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="modal-dialog" role="document">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <div class="modal-header">
                <h5 class="modal-title" id="helpModalLabel">Photo Delay Help</h5>
                <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close">
                    <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
                </button>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-body">
            <h4> More info: </h4>
                <p>You can use a stopwatch to get this value, <b>Start</b> when UV turns off and <b>Stop</b> when the buildplate reaches the up most top before coming down again.</p>
            	<p>If you get values like 4.32 sec, round it dowsn for exemple to 4 sec. </p>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-footer">
                <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<hr>
<div class="control-group"> <!-- Added -->
    <label class="control-label" for="timeout">Timeout (seconds):</label>
    <div class="controls">
        <input type="number" class="form-control input-sm" style="width: 50px;" id="timeput" min="1" step="1" data-bind="value: settings.plugins.slatimelapse.timeout">
        <span class="info-icon">
            <a href="#" class="same-color" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#helpModalTimeout"> <!-- Added data-toggle and data-target attributes -->
                <img src="/plugin/slatimelapse/static/img/info.png" alt="Information">
            </a>
        </span>
        <p class="help-block">Enter the timeout value (in seconds) after last layer to generate Video File.</p>
    </div>
</div>
<!-- Modal -->
<div class="modal fade" id="helpModalTimeout" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="helpModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="modal-dialog" role="document">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <div class="modal-header">
                <h5 class="modal-title" id="helpModalLabel">Photo Delay Help</h5>
                <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close">
                    <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
                </button>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-body">
            <h4> More info: </h4>
                <p>This value refers to the amount of time that has to pass before if cancels/finished the current Job due to inactivity of since last layer.</p>
            	<p>After this timeout, Sla Timelapse will generate a video file and save it !</p>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-footer">
                <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<hr>
<div>
<button type="button" class="btn btn-primary" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#ldrCableModal">Make LDR Cable</button> <!-- Button for LDR Cable -->
</div>
<!-- Modal for LDR Cable -->
<div class="modal fade" id="ldrCableModal" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="ldrCableModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="modal-dialog" role="document">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <div class="modal-header">
                <h5 class="modal-title" id="ldrCableModalLabel">Make LDR Cable</h5>
                <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close">
                    <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
                </button>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-body">
                <img src="/plugin/slatimelapse/static/img/ldr_cable.png" alt="LDR Cable Image">
            </div>
            <div class="modal-footer">
                <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

</td>
<td>
		<a href="">
		    <img src="/plugin/slatimelapse/static/img/slatimelapse.png" alt="Description of the image">
		</a>
</td>
</tr>
